Class DbEntity

Namespace
NDSH.Database.Entities
Assembly
NDSH.Models.dll

Serves as the base class for database entities, providing an integer identifier DbId and optional constructor-based ID assignment. Inherit from this class to create custom entities that integrate with frameworks requiring a unique integer key.

public abstract class DbEntity : Model, IModel, IDbId, IHashCode
